      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Isolated Agents, Isolated Failures: The Case for Sandboxed Operations</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">When an agent makes a mistake, the blast radius matters more than the mistake itself. A typo in a draft email is harmless. A bad database query that corrupts production data is catastrophic. The single most important architectural decision in agent deployment is isolation.</p>
